RED has started selling new Raven camera bundles on Apple’s website. The Raven is RED’s “budget” 4.5K camera, and the Apple bundle is going for $14,999. The package contains the 4.5K 120fps RED Raven camera, Sigma 13-35mm F1.8 “Art” lens, 4.7-inch touch LCD monitor, two 120GB SSDs, batteries, charger, Nanuk heavy-duty case, and an outrigger handle. Apple also includes Final Cut Pro X with the package. “The RED Raven Camera Kit gives you all the components you need to begin shooting true professional-quality video,” said Apple.